jZ7.jpg"},"name":"深町寿成","short_summary":"深町 寿成（ふかまち としなり、8月29日 - ）は、日本の声優。アプトプロ所属。山形県出身。","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":20811,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":44922},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/6e/86/44923_crt_iniVP.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6e/86/44923_crt_iniVP.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/6e/86/44923_crt_iniVP.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/6e/86/44923_crt_iniVP.jpg"},"name":"マキハラユキ","summary":"ライアーゲームの参加者。落ち着いた雰囲気の女性。","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/33/9d/32683_prsn_Rc6tn.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/33/9d/32683_prsn_Rc6tn.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/33/9d/32683_prsn_Rc6tn.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/33/9d/32683_prsn_Rc6tn.jpg"},"name":"胡麻鶴彩","short_summary":"","career":["seiyu"],"id":32683,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":44923},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/9e/94/44927_crt_jHJpG.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/9e/94/44927_crt_jHJpG.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/9e/94/44927_crt_jHJpG.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/9e/94/44927_crt_jHJpG.jpg"},"name":"福永ユウジ","summary":"ライアーゲームの参加者。華やかな雰囲気を漂わせ、積極的に人と接する女性。","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/f0/96/10869_prsn_nWIUY.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f0/96/10869_prsn_nWIUY.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/f0/96/10869_prsn_nWIUY.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/f0/96/10869_prsn_nWIUY.jpg"},"name":"大地葉","short_summary":"日本女性声优，埼玉县出生。日本播音演技研究所出身，隶属于VIMS。名字“大地叶”（たいち よう／Taichi You）是艺名，由来是学生时期的绰号たいちょー（“队长”，日语读音：Taichō）。\r\n\r\n趣味・特技：インド映画鑑賞、ピアノ弾き語り、曲のコピー（譜面をおこせる）\r\n芸歴：日本ナレーション演技研究所","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":10869,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":44927},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/e8/2d/44937_crt_8BqTT.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bg